alert.note: Alert for Eastern Juab, Millard Counties (Utah) Issued by the National Weather Service

info.headline: High Wind Warning issued June 18 at 3:14PM MDT until June 20 at 12:00AM MDT by NWS Saltlake
info.description: ...WIND ADVISORY REMAINS IN EFFECT UNTIL MIDNIGHT MDT TONIGHT... ...HIGH WIND WARNING IN EFFECT FROM 10 AM MONDAY TO MIDNIGHT MDT MONDAY NIGHT... * WHAT...For the High Wind Warning, southwest winds 25 to 35 mph with gusts up to 60 mph expected. For the Wind Advisory, southwest winds 20 to 30 mph with gusts up to 50 mph. * WHERE...Eastern Juab/Millard Counties. * WHEN...For the High Wind Warning, from 10 AM Monday to midnight MDT Monday night. For the Wind Advisory, until midnight MDT tonight. * IMPACTS...High winds may move loose debris, damage property and cause power outages. Travel will be difficult due to crosswinds, especially for high profile vehicles and vehicles with trailers.
info.instruction: People are urged to secure loose objects that could be blown around or damaged by the wind.
